<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>posts on A'Khun</title><link>https://akhun.co/posts/</link><description>Recent content in posts on A'Khun</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://akhun.co/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>全民台語認證準備心得</title><link>https://akhun.co/posts/2018/%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%B0%E8%AA%9E%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/</link><pubDate>Thu, 26 Jul 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://akhun.co/posts/2018/%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%B0%E8%AA%9E%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/</guid><description>&lt;p>本來只打算分享今年考 &lt;a href="http://ctlt.twl.ncku.edu.tw/gtpt/index.html">全民台語認證&lt;/a> 的心得，但因為我準備期太短了，不把過去的成長背景放進來看，會覺得這成績太扯，所以就一起寫吧！&lt;/p>

